      "content": "\"let go of the futile struggle\"... that's a heavy way to put it. do you mean like just giving up on everything? like, if there really is no point to any of this, then what's actually the difference between struggling through it all or just... stopping? it feels like there's a certain logic to just stopping, doesn't there?",
